    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "I can't help but wonder if there is a real product bug here such that we're closing either the websocket, yamux session, or coordinate stream immediately after sending `Disconnect`, and this is causing the message not to make it to the server.\r\n\r\nWe should send disconnect, and then wait for the server to hang up on us.",
